Key = "skill"
Title = "Skills"
Description = "Skills are techniques that can be used in [?combat]combat[/?] to inflict [?damage]damage[/?], [?heal]heal[/?] or move. Humans have a walk skill, and 3 personnal skills - one from each of their parent, and a third one determined randomly.
Skills usually have an [?element]element[/?], a cast range, an area of effect, and an effect. Appart from walking, using one passes the character's turn."
